  "text": "The DPPIV enzymatic activity was assessed in the serum and heart homogenate by measuring the release of p-nitroaniline resulting from the hydrolysis of glycylproline p-nitroanilide tosylate, as previously described [CITATION_1] . The heart DPPIV abundance was analyzed using immunoblotting and quantitative RT-PCR.",
